folder: Moffat Street & Bushwick Avenue, Brooklyn, NY
text:
(1) Moffat Street, east side, between Bushwick Ave., and Broadway, showing the church and adjacent buildings, of the German Evangelical Home for the Aged. January 1925. Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(2) The same, another view from the opposite direction. January 1925. Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
